      },
      "message": "Add drug discovery (dd) evaluation suite under evaluations/dd\n\nImports the Agent4Science molecular & protein benchmark: 79 tasks across\n5 categories (C1 preprocessing, C2 analysis, C3 optimization, C4 safety,\nC5 claim validation) with a unified CLI (evaluate.py), shared runners\n(batch / notebook / design), category scorers, and reference example\nagents. Ignored files (.env, results/, __pycache__/, .venv/) are excluded.",
