        "date": "2026-04-16T17:11:20Z"
      },
      "message": "Add ToolUniverse agent template under agentdir/ToolUniverse\n\nDrops a prompt in, returns generated .py + full .txt run log using\nChatGPT function calls grounded in ToolUniverse. Includes:\n\n- run_prompt.py       single-prompt runner (prompt -> .py + .txt)\n- run_pipeline.py     multi-step runner (# TASK headers -> onestep.py + logs)\n- _agent_core.py      shared LLM client / tool loop helpers\n- prompts/            example single prompts and full scRNA/spatial pipelines\n- README.md           English usage + provider config\n- .env.example + .gitignore so credentials never land in the repo\n\nMade-with: Cursor",
      "tree": {
